org.revapi

Interface ElementForest.Visitor<E extends Element<E>>

  • Enclosing interface:
    ElementForest<E extends Element<E>>

    public static interface ElementForest.Visitor<E extends Element<E>>
    A visitor of the element forest. Passed to the ElementForest.walk(Element, Visitor) so that the callers can easily walk the forest.
